originalText.text:
Paddington is the most helpful agent I have worked with in NYC. She knows how to get things done. From the beginning, her upfront honesty and straightforwardness was greatly appreciated.

She is a true real estate professional who brings breadth and depth of knowledge. She is straightforward, transparent, and does what it takes to move things forward. Her track record is a representation of how she has been able find great opportunities for everyone she works with and will continue to do so.

Paddington also is well aware of the market and where things stand, finding the middle ground for all parties. She does the hardest parts of the job masterfully and prioritizes communication, clarity, and help for all involved. I plan to continue to work with Paddington into the future and enjoyed the experience I had overall!

originalText.text: Paddington is a great partner.  She knows the Manhattan downtown market extremely well; she’s a pro.  Her insight with respect to my condo sale started a full year before I was ready to put my condo on the market.  She advised me on the type of renovations that would make my condo more attractive, and even on which features/styles buyers were looking for in my immediate neighborhood.  And when it came time to list my condo, Paddington was relentless in finding creative ways to attract buyers.  She kept me in the know about every step in the process, and ultimately found me the perfect buyer who met all my needs. She is a master of buyer/seller fit.  I would definitely partner with Paddington again!

originalText.text: Paddington is a standout broker with a wealth of knowledge! Her expertise in design and build is super impressive, and the way she manages everything for international clients is top-notch. Even without being in the same country, she ensures every detail is taken care of with utmost precision. If you need a reliable, knowledgeable, and thorough real estate professional, Paddington is definitely the one.
